For an energy eigenstate $bar.v n chevron.r$ of the harmonic oscillator, what is the value of $sigma_x sigma_p$?
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$(n+1/2) planck$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$(n+1) planck / 2$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$planck / 2$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: a_width, margin: a_margin)
#set text(size: a_size)
$n planck$
#pagebreak()
#set page(width: i_width, height: auto, margin: i_margin)
#set text(size: i_size)
Explanation:

For eigenstates, $sigma_x sigma_p = (n+1/2) planck$. The minimum value is $planck/2$ for the ground state.
